Notes : Color code meaning :
u No timezone and language translation options available Group Standing Table (on player prediction board)
u You can change the date manuallly in tournament actual result table above Q Qualify and Correct Position
u You can change the country's name to your own language by replacing their names in the table in Team Setup worksheet Q Qualify but Incorrect Position
Knock Out Matches
u All matches are sorted based on FIFA World Cup match number T Correct Bracket Pairing (on player prediction board if player's prediction matches is chosen)
Some matches with greater match number shall be played ahead of lower match number T Knock Out Match Winner (all matches)
u Check your score input, incorrect score input will make an error in Excel formula calculation Score Boxes
u Input full time score results (Normal Time + Extra Time) in FT score boxes in knock out round matches o Incorrect score input (text) (all matches)
u PSO (Penalty Shoot Out score boxes will be shown automatically for respective matches if there are no winners in FULL TIME regulation Last Group Matches
  1 column x 16 rows bar at the left side of each player prediction boxes is the marker bar
u Bonus points 1-9 will be shown after all group matches are completed and players type scores for all group matches score boxes along that rows must be filled to mark that all group matches are completed and to activate bonus points
